<p>The Municipal Land Transfer Tax Calculator can only be used if the terms and conditions are agreed to. If you do not
  agree with the terms and conditions but would like to find out more information regarding Municipal Land Transfer Tax,
  contact:</p>
<div class=\"well\"><p>Call 311 – Tax & Utility Inquiry Line</p>
  <ul class=\"list-unstyled\">
    <li>Within city limits, call 311</li>
    <li>Outside city limits, call 416-392-CITY (2489)</li>
    <li>TTY: 416-392-0719</li>
    <li>Monday – Friday, 8 a.m. – 6 p.m.</li>
  </ul>
</div><p>or</p>
